      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/23/2/222/1",
      "text": [
        ": مَنْ قَرَأَ سُورَهَ الصَّفِّ وَ أَدْمَنَ قِرَاءَتَهَا فِی فَرَائِضِهِ وَ نَوَافِلِهِ صَفَّهُ اللَّهُ مَعَ مَلَائِکَتِهِ وَ أَنْبِیَائِهِ الْمُرْسَلِینَ إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1. From the previous chain from al-Hassan from his father from Abi Basir from Abi Ja’far (a.s.) who said: One who recites Surah Saff and is regular in reciting it in the obligatory prayers, Allah includes him in the row of His angels, prophets and messengers, Insha Allah."
        ]
      }
